<h4>Troubleshooting</h4>
<p>
   KCPRMP3 is the only one that will work with Windows Media Player.
   iTunes and WinAmp should work on all three.
</p>

<p>
   The stream URLs probably won't play in a browser. Instead, look for a "open location" menu in your media player and paste the link.
</p>

<p>
   Some browsers don't open the m3u redirectors correctly, so try right-clicking to download the file, and run it from your computer.
